    "subtype": "equipment",
    "text": "This large *+2 striking standard-grade silver bastard sword* is the signature weapon of many veteran Eagle Knights. It\u2019s easily recognized by its distinctively notched blade and the stylized wings adorning its cross guard. These blades are sometimes passed down from generation to generation.",
    "traits": [
      {
        "alternate_link": {
