        "subtype": "equipment",
        "text": "Eagle Knights charged with protecting Andoran\u2019s western border against Chelaxian incursion often carry these +2 greater striking standard-grade silver bastard swords, enchanted to offer greater utility when battling fiends. A greater talonstrike blade gains the Grasping Talons activation.",
